ame field is empty.'=>'<strong>错误</strong>：用户名字段为空。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: The password field is empty.'=>'<strong>错误</strong>：密码字段为空。','Email address does not match the allowed hosted domain'=>'电子邮件地址与允许的托管域不匹配','The authentication timestamp is too old, please try again.'=>'身份验证时间戳太旧，请重试。','Invalid Google credentials provided.'=>'提供的 Google 凭据无效。','Google credentials do not match the allowed hosted domain'=>'Google 凭据与允许的托管域不匹配','CAS server returned an Authentication Exception. Details:'=>'CAS 服务器返回身份验证异常。详：','[%s] Attempting to authenticate via LDAP.'=>'[%s]尝试通过 LDAP 进行身份验证。','Failed: no LDAP Host(s) specified.'=>'失败：未指定 LDAP 主机。','Failed: no LDAP Search Base(s) specified.'=>'失败：未指定LDAP搜索库。','Failed: empty username and password.'=>'失败：用户名和密码为空。','Failed: empty username.'=>'失败：用户名为空。','You must provide a username or email.'=>'您必须提供用户名或电子邮件。','Failed: empty password.'=>'失败：密码为空。','You must provide a password.'=>'您必须提供密码。','Failed: php-ldap extension not installed.'=>'失败：未安装 php-ldap 扩展。','Warning: could not parse host %s with wp_parse_url().'=>'警告：无法使用 wp_parse_url（） 解析主机 %s。','Warning: syntax check failed on host %s in ldap_connect().'=>'警告：在 ldap_connect（） 中对主机 %s 进行语法检查失败。','Warning: unable to start TLS on host %s:'=>'警告：无法在主机 %s 上启动 TLS：','Performing bind as user logging in: %s.'=>'以用户身份登录时执行绑定：%s。','Warning: unable to bind on host %1$s using directory user:'=>'警告：无法使用目录用户绑定主机 %1$s：','Successful bind using LDAP user DN %s instead of directory user.'=>'使用 LDAP 用户 DN %s 而不是目录用户成功绑定。','Failed: password incorrect for LDAP user %s.'=>'失败：LDAP 用户 %s 的密码不正确。','Connected to LDAP host %s.'=>'已连接到 LDAP 主机 %s。','Failed: unable to connect to any LDAP host.'=>'失败：无法连接到任何 LDAP 主机。','Using LDAP search filter: %s'=>'使用 LDAP 搜索过滤器： %s','Found user %1$s in search base: %2$s'=>'在搜索库中找到用户 %1$s： %2$s','Failed to find user %1$s in %2$s. Trying next search base.'=>'未能在 %2$s 中找到用户 %1$s。尝试下一个搜索库。','Failed: no LDAP user %s found.'=>'失败：未找到 LDAP 用户 %s。','[%1$s] Successfully authenticated user %2$s (%3$s) via LDAP.'=>'[%1$s]已通过 LDAP 成功对用户 %2$s （%3$s） 进行身份验证。','%s - Access Restricted'=>'%s - 访问受限','Back'=>'返回','Invalid login attempted.'=>'尝试的登录无效。','Action required: Pending user %1$s at %2$s'=>'所需操作：待处理用户 %1$s at %2$s','A new user has tried to access the %1$s site you manage at:
