','Notice: You are browsing this site anonymously, and only have access to a portion of its content.'=>'注意：您是匿名浏览本网站，只能访问其部分内容。','Manage who has access to this site using these lists.'=>'使用这些列表管理谁有权访问此站点。','<strong>Pending</strong> users are users who have successfully logged in to the site, but who haven\'t yet been approved (or blocked) by you.'=>'<strong>待处理</strong>用户是指已成功登录网站但尚未获得您的批准（或阻止）的用户。','<strong>Approved</strong> users have access to the site once they successfully log in.'=>'<strong>获得批准</strong>的用户在成功登录后即可访问该站点。','<strong>Blocked</strong> users will receive an error message when they try to visit the site after authenticating.'=>'<strong>被阻止</strong>的用户在身份验证后尝试访问该站点时将收到错误消息。','Note: if you want to block all email addresses from a domain, say anyone@example.com, simply add "@example.com" to the blocked list.'=>'注意：如果您想阻止域中的所有电子邮件地址，例如 anyone@example.com，只需将“@example.com”添加到阻止列表中即可。','Approve'=>'批准','Block'=>'禁用','Ignore'=>'忽视','No pending users'=>'没有待处理的用户','email address'=>'电子邮件地址','Toggle Dropdown'=>'切换下拉列表','Create a new WordPress account, and email the user an activation link.'=>'创建一个新的 WordPress 帐户，并通过电子邮件向用户发送激活链接。','Current Page'=>'当前页面','paging%1$s of %2$s'=>'%1$s 的 %2$s','Search Users'=>'搜索用户','Search'=>'搜索','-- None --'=>'--没有--','You may optionally specify some advanced settings below.'=>'您可以选择在下面指定一些高级设置。','After'=>'之后','invalid password attempts, delay further attempts on that user for'=>'无效的密码尝试，延迟对该用户的进一步尝试','minute(s).'=>'分钟(s)。','more invalid attempts, increase the delay to'=>'无效尝试越多，延迟增加到','minutes.'=>'分钟。','Reset the delays after'=>'重置延迟后','minutes with no invalid attempts.'=>'没有无效尝试的分钟数。','Note: You can always access the WordPress logins by adding external=wordpress to the wp-login URL, like so:'=>'注意：您始终可以通过将 external=wordpress 添加到 wp-login URL 来访问 WordPress 登录名，如下所示：','Warning: Disabling WordPress logins means you will not be able to access WordPress administration if your external service(s) are not working. Use with caution. Note: If no external services are enabled, WordPress logins will not be disabled.'=>'警告：禁用 WordPress 登录意味着如果您的外部服务无法正常工作，您将无法访问 WordPress 管理。请谨慎使用。注意：如果未启用外部服务，则不会禁用WordPress登录。','Default WordPress login screen'=>'默认 WordPress 登录屏幕','<strong>Note for theme developers</strong>: Add more options here by using the `authorizer_add_branding_option` filter in your theme. You can see an example theme that implements this filter in the plugin directory under sample-theme-add-branding.'=>'<strong>模版开发者注意事项</strong>：在此处使用模版中的“authorizer_add_branding_option”过滤器添加更多选项。您可以在 sample-theme-add-branding 下的插件目录中看到实现此过滤器的示例主题。','Show in Settings menu'=>'在“设置”菜单中显示','Show in sidebar (top level)'=>'在侧边栏中显示（顶层）','All Usermeta:'=>'所有用户meta：','Date approved'=>'批准日期','Email'=>'电子邮件','Role'=>'角色','Date registered'=>'注册日期','Ascending'=>'顺序','Descending'=>'倒序','Note: Only users with the create_users capability will be able to see the dashboard widget.'=>'注意：只有具有create_users功能的用户才能看到仪表板小组件。','Configure this site independently (don\'t inherit any multisite settings)'=>'独立配置此站点（不继承任何多站点设置）','Enter your external server settings below.'=>'在下面输入您的外部服务器设置。','Choose who is able to log into this site below.'=>'在下面选择谁可以登录此站点。','All authenticated users (All external service users and all WordPress users)'=>'所有经过身份验证的用户（所有外部服务用户和所有 WordPress 用户）','Only'=>'只有','approved users'=>'审核的用户','(Approved external users and all WordPress users)'=>'（经批准的外部用户和所有 WordPress 用户）','None (Don\'t send notification emails)'=>'无（不发送通知电子邮件）','Send a welcome email when approving a new user'=>'批准新用户时发送欢迎电子邮件','You can use the <b>[site_name]</b> shortcode.'=>'您可以使用 <b>[site_name]</b> 短代码。','You can use %1$s, %2$s, and %3$s shortcodes.'=>'可以使用 %1$s、%2$s 和 %3$s 短代码。','Choose your public access options here.'=>'在此处选择您的公共访问选项。','Everyone can see the site'=>'每个人都可以看到该网站','Only logged in users can see the site'=>'只有登录用户才能看到该站点','Send them to the login screen'=>'将它们发送到登录屏幕','Show them the anonymous access message (below)'=>'向他们展示匿名访问消息（如下）','Show them the page <strong>without</strong> the anonymous access message'=>'向他们显示<strong>没有</strong>匿名访问消息的页面','Show them the page <strong>with</strong> the anonymous access message (marked up as a <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/components/#alerts-dismissible" target="_blank">Bootstrap Dismissible Alert</a>)'=>'向他们展示<strong>带有</strong>匿名访问消息的页面（标记为<a href=“http://getbootstrap.com/components/#alerts-dismissible” target=“_blank”>Bootstrap Dismissible Alert</a>）','Home'=>'主页','Home Page'=>'主页','Nonexistent (404) Pages'=>'不存在 （404） 页','Categories'=>'类别','<a href="http://www.php.net//manual/en/curl.installation.php" target="_blank" style="color: #dc3232;">PHP CURL extension</a> is not installed'=>'<a href=“http://www.php.net//manual/en/curl.installation.php” target=“_blank” style=“color： #dc3232;”>PHP CURL 扩展</a>未安装','<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/23424459/enable-php-openssl-not-working" target="_blank" style="color: #dc3232;">PHP openssl extension</a> is not installed'=>'<a href=“http://stackoverflow.com/questions/23424459/enable-php-openssl-not-working” target=“_blank” style=“color： #dc3232;”>PHP openssl extension</a> 未安装','Warning'=>'警告','Enable CAS Logins'=>'启用 CAS 登录','The button on the login page will read:'=>'登录页面上的按钮将显示：','Sign in with'=>'登录方式','Example:  authn.example.edu'=>'示例：authn.example.edu','Example:  443'=>'示例：443','Example:  /cas'=>'示例：/cas','"Client" is the most common, but use "Proxy" if your CAS server is behind a proxy server.'=>'“客户端”是最常见的，但如果 CAS 服务器位于代理服务器后面，请使用“代理”。','Example:  mail'=>'示例：邮件','Note: If your CAS server doesn\'t return an attribute containing an email, you can specify the @domain portion of the email address here, and the email address will be constructed from it and the username. For example, if user \'bob\' logs in and his email address should be bob@example.edu, then enter <strong>@example.edu</strong> in this field.'=>'注意：如果您的 CAS 服务器未返回包含电子邮件的属性，您可以在此处指定电子邮件地址的@domain部分，电子邮件地址将根据该部分和用户名构建。例如，如果用户“bob”登录并且他的电子邮件地址应 bob@example.edu，则在此字段中输入 <strong>@example.edu</strong>。','Example:  givenName'=>'示例：givenName','Example:  sn'=>'示例：sn','Do not update first and last name fields on login'=>'登录时不更新名字和姓氏字段','Update first and last name fields on login'=>'更新登录时的名字和姓氏字段','Update first and last name fields on login only if they are empty'=>'仅当名字和姓氏字段为空时，才更新登录时的名字和姓氏字段','Immediately redirect to CAS login form if it\'s the only enabled external service and WordPress logins are hidden'=>'如果它是唯一启用的外部服务，并且 WordPress 登录名被隐藏，请立即重定向到 CAS 登录表单','Note: This feature will only work if you have checked "Hide WordPress Logins" in Advanced settings, and if CAS is the only enabled service (i.e., no Google or LDAP). If you have enabled CAS Single Sign-On (SSO), and a user has already logged into CAS elsewhere, enabling this feature will allow automatic logins without any user interaction.'=>'注意：仅当您在高级设置中选中了“隐藏 WordPress 登录”，并且 CAS 是唯一启用的服务（即没有 Google 或 LDAP）时，此功能才有效。如果已启用 CAS 单点登录 （SSO），并且用户已在其他位置登录 CAS，则启用此功能将允许自动登录，而无需任何用户交互。','Link CAS accounts to WordPress accounts by their username (leave this off to link by email address)'=>'通过用户名将 CAS 帐户链接到 WordPress 帐户（将其保留为按电子邮件地址链接）','Note: The default (and most secure) behavior is to associate WordPress accounts with CAS accounts by the email they have in common. However, some uncommon CAS server configurations don\'t contain email addresses for users. Enable this option if your CAS server doesn\'t have an attribute containing an email, or if you have WordPress accounts that don\'t have emails.'=>'注意：默认（也是最安全的）行为是通过 WordPress 帐户与 CAS 帐户的共同电子邮件相关联。但是，某些不常见的 CAS 服务器配置不包含用户的电子邮件地址。如果您的 CAS 服务器没有包含电子邮件的属性，或者您的 WordPress 帐户没有电子邮件，请启用此选项。','Enable Google Logins'=>'启用 Google 登录','If you don\'t have a Google Client ID and Secret, generate them by following these instructions:'=>'如果您没有 Google 客户端 ID 和密钥，请按照以下说明生成它们：','Click <strong>Create a Project</strong> on the <a href="https://cloud.google.com/console" target="_blank">Google Cloud Console</a>. You can name it whatever you want.'=>'点击 <a href=“https://cloud.google.com/console” target=“_blank”>Google Cloud Console 上的<strong>创建项目</strong></a>。您可以随心所欲地命名它。','Within the project, navigate to <em>APIs and Services</em> &gt; <em>Credentials</em>, then click <strong>+ Create Credentials &gt; OAuth client ID</strong>. Use these settings:'=>'在项目中，导航到“<em>API 和服务</em>”&gt;<em>“凭据</em>”，然后单击“<strong>+ 创建凭据”&gt; OAuth 客户端 ID“</strong>。使用以下设置：','Application Type: <strong>Web application</strong>'=>'应用程序类型：<strong>Web 应用程序</strong>','Authorized Javascript Origins:'=>'授权的 Javascript 来源：','Authorized Redirect URI: <em>none</em>'=>'授权重定向 URI：<em>无</em>','Copy/paste your new Client ID/Secret pair into the fields below.'=>'将新的客户端 ID/密钥对复制/粘贴到以下字段中。','<strong>Note</strong>: Navigate to <em>APIs and Services</em> &gt; <em>OAuth consent screen</em> to change the way the Google consent screen appears after a user has successfully entered their password, but before they are redirected back to WordPress.'=>'<strong>注意</strong>：在用户成功输入密码后，但在用户<em></em>被重定向回 WordPress 之前，导航&gt; <em>API 和服务</em>，以更改 Google 同意屏幕的显示方式。','Note: Google may have a more recent version of these instructions in their <a href="https://developers.google.com/identity/gsi/web" target="_blank">developer documentation</a>.'=>'注意：Google 的 <a href=“https://developers.google.com/identity/gsi/web” target=“_blank”>开发者文档中可能提供了这些说明的最新版本</a>。','Example:  1234567890123-kdjr85yt6vjr6d8g7dhr8g7d6durjf7g.apps.googleusercontent.com'=>'示例：1234567890123-kdjr85yt6vjr6d8g7dhr8g7d6durjf7g.apps.googleusercontent.com','This setting is not editable since it has been defined in the %s filter.'=>'此设置不可编辑，因为它已在 %s 筛选器中定义。','This setting is not editable since it has been defined in wp-config.php via %s'=>'此设置不可编辑，因为它已通过 %s 在 wp-config.php 中定义','Example:  sDNgX5_pr_5bly-frKmvp8jT'=>'示例：sDNgX5_pr_5bly-frKmvp8jT','Restrict Google logins to a specific Google Apps hosted domain (for example, mycollege.edu). Leave blank to allow all Google sign-ins.'=>'将 Google 登录限制为特定的 Google Apps 托管域（例如 mycollege.edu）。留空以允许所有 Google 登录。','If restricting to multiple domains, add one domain per line.'=>'如果限制为多个域，则每行添加一个域。','Warning: <a href="http://www.php.net/manual/en/ldap.installation.php" target="_blank" style="color: #dc3232;">PHP LDAP extension</a> is <strong>not</strong> installed'=>'警告：<a href=“http://www.php.net/manual/en/ldap.installation.php” target=“_blank” style=“color： #dc3232;”>PHP LDAP 扩展</a><strong>未</strong>安装','Enable LDAP Logins'=>'启用 LDAP 登录','Specify either a hostname (for example, ldap.example.edu) or a full LDAP URI (for example, ldaps://ldap.example.edu:636).'=>'指定主机名（例如，ldap.example.edu）或完整的 LDAP URI（例如，ldaps://ldap.example.edu:636）。','If you have multiple LDAP servers (failover or high-availability configuration), separate them by newlines (one per line).'=>'如果您有多个 LDAP 服务器（故障转移或高可用性配置），请用换行符（每行一个）分隔它们。','Example:  389'=>'示例：389','If a full LDAP URI (ldaps://hostname:port) is specified above, this field is ignored.'=>'如果上面指定了完整的 LDAP URI （ldaps：//hostname：port），则忽略此字段。','If an ldaps:// URL (and therefore Implicit TLS) is used, this checkbox is ignored.'=>'如果使用 ldaps:// URL（因此使用隐式 TLS），则忽略此复选框。','Example:  ou=people,dc=example,dc=edu'=>'示例：ou=people，dc=example，dc=edu','If you have multiple search bases, separate them by newlines (one per line).'=>'如果您有多个搜索库，请用换行符分隔它们（每行一个）。','Example:  (memberOf=cn=wp_users,ou=people,dc=example,dc=edu)'=>'示例：（memberOf=cn=wp_users，ou=people，dc=example，dc=edu）','If you wish to use an LDAP search filter, enter it here. Otherwise leave this field blank.'=>'如果您希望使用 LDAP 搜索过滤器，请在此处输入。否则，请将此字段留空。','Example:  uid'=>'示例：uid','Note: If your LDAP server doesn\'t return an attribute containing an email, you can specify the @domain portion of the email address here, and the email address will be constructed from it and the username. For example, if user \'bob\' logs in and his email address should be bob@example.edu, then enter <strong>@example.edu</strong> in this field.'=>'注意：如果您的 LDAP 服务器未返回包含电子邮件的属性，您可以在此处指定电子邮件地址的@domain部分，电子邮件地址将根据它和用户名构建。例如，如果用户“bob”登录并且他的电子邮件地址应 bob@example.edu，则在此字段中输入 <strong>@example.edu</strong>。','Example:  cn=directory-user,ou=specials,dc=example,dc=edu'=>'示例：cn=directory-user，ou=specials，dc=example，dc=edu','Note: You can use the %s wildcard to bind as the username of the user logging in instead of a directory user service account.'=>'注意：您可以使用 %s 通配符绑定为登录用户的用户名，而不是目录用户服务帐户。','Example: <strong>uid=%s,ou=people,dc=example,dc=edu</strong>.'=>'示例：<strong>uid=%s，ou=people，dc=example，dc=edu</strong>。','Leave the LDAP Directory User Password field below blank, and the bind will be attempted with the user-supplied password.'=>'将“LDAP 目录用户密码”字段留空，将尝试使用用户提供的密码进行绑定。','Example:  https://myschool.example.edu:8888/am-forgot-password'=>'示例：https://myschool.example.edu:8888/am-forgot-password','Example:  givenname'=>'示例：givenname','username'=>'用户名','password'=>'密码','Test'=>'测试','Note: Make sure to save any changes to LDAP settings before clicking the Test button.'=>'注意：在单击“测试”按钮之前，请确保保存对 LDAP 设置所做的任何更改。','Enable OAuth2 Logins'=>'启用 OAuth2 登录','Generate your Client ID and Secret for your selected provider by following their specific instructions.'=>'按照其特定说明为所选提供商生成客户端 ID 和密钥。','If asked for a redirect or callback URL, use:'=>'如果要求提供重定向或回调 URL，请使用：','If using Microsoft Azure, omit the querystring; use:'=>'如果使用 Microsoft Azure，请省略查询字符串;用：','Example:  0123456789abcdef0123'=>'示例：0123456789abcdef0123','Example:  0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef'=>'示例：0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef','Restrict OAuth2 logins to a specific domain (for example, mycollege.edu). Leave blank to allow all valid sign-ins.'=>'将 OAuth2 登录限制为特定域（例如，mycollege.edu）。留空以允许所有有效登录。','Example:  "common", or a specific Azure Directory Tenant ID'=>'示例：“common”，或特定的 Azure 目录租户 ID','Example:  https://example.edu/login/oauth/authorize'=>'如: https://example.edu/login/oauth/authorize','Example:  https://example.edu/login/oauth/access_token'=>'如: https://example.edu/login/oauth/access_token','Example:  https://api.example.edu/user'=>'如: https://api.example.edu/user','Authorizer'=>'授权管理','https://github.com/uhm-coe/authorizer'=>'https://github.com/uhm-coe/authorizer','Authorizer limits login attempts, restricts access to specified users, and authenticates against external sources (e.g., OAuth2, Google, LDAP, or CAS).'=>'授权方限制登录尝试，限制对指定用户的访问，并针对外部源（例如 OAuth2、Google、LDAP 或 CAS）进行身份验证。','Paul Ryan <prar@hawaii.edu>'=>'保罗·瑞安（Paul Ryan）<prar@hawaii.edu>'],'language'=>'zh_CN','x-generator'=>'Poedit 3.4.4'];